videos.description: Zack Mahoney run for 2-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Syracuse gets on the board first with QB keeper

videos.description: Peterman hits Jester Weah on the slant and he does the rest going 59-yard to the end zone for a Pitt touchdown.
videos.headline: Weah races through the defense for 59-yard TD

videos.description: Pitt WR Aaron Matthews lays out for the catch but deflects it to Cuse corner Corey Winfield who makes the interception for return for no gain to the Syrac 33
videos.headline: Cuse corner Corey Winfield makes pick off deflection

videos.description: Sterling Hofrichter punt for 39-yards , Quadree Henderson returns for 39-yards to the Syrac 35
videos.headline: Quadree Henderson shows fancy footwork on 39-yard punt return

videos.description: Pittsburgh QB Nathan Peterman passes to an open James Conner who races into the end zone for a 35-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Pitt takes lead with Conner 35-yard TD reception

videos.description: Zack Mahoney pass complete to Steve Ishmael for 62-yards to the Pitt 3 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Cuse WR Ishmael goes over the top for incredible catch

videos.description: Dontae Strickland run for 5-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Cuse evens the score on Strickland run

videos.description: Nathan Peterman run for 9-yards to the Syrac 19 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Pitt QB Peterman shakes off big hit for first down

videos.description: George Aston run for 6-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Pitt takes lead on jet sweep by FB Alston

videos.description: Quadree Henderson run for 34-yards to the Syrac 30 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Henderson turns on the jets on 34-yard run

videos.description: Pitt takes 14-point lead on James Conner run for 9-yards for a TD
videos.headline: James Conner gets upended on 9-yard TD run

videos.description: Zack Mahoney pass complete to Amba Etta-Tawo for 5-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Cuse within seven after screen to Etta-Tawo

videos.description: Nathan Peterman run for 13-yards for a TD. Call of TD is confirmed after review.
videos.headline: Pitt QB Peterman takes flight on 13-yard TD scramble

videos.description: Syracuse QB Zack Mahoney's pass is intercepted and returned 20 yards for a touchdown by Pittsburgh DB Dane Jackson.
videos.headline: Pitt DB takes interception 20 yards for the pick-six

videos.description: Quadree Henderson run for 66-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Pitt RB Hendersons' wheels on full display on 66-yard TD run

videos.description: Moe Neal run for 42-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Cuse answers Pitt score with big TD run of their own

videos.description: Pittsburgh WR Maurice Ffrench takes an end-around and races past Syracuse's defense scoring a 77-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Pitt piles on Syracuse, scores 77-yard TD

videos.description: Zack Mahoney pass complete to Amba Etta-Tawo for 12-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Etta-Tawo tip-toes way into end zone for second score

videos.description: Nathan Peterman run for a loss of 1-yard to the Syrac 37 Nathan Peterman fumbled, forced by Jonathan Thomas, recovered by Syrac Chris Slayton
videos.headline: Orange recovers after Pitt QB Peterman fumbles on blindside hit

videos.description: Zack Mahoney run for 19-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Mahoney does it himself, goes 19-yards for the TD

videos.description: Zack Mahoney pass complete to Amba Etta-Tawo for 7-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Amba Etta-Tawo hauls in third TD reception of game

videos.description: James Conner run for 34-yards to the Syrac 7 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: James Conner breaks off another big run

videos.description: Nathan Peterman pass complete to Jester Weah for 6-yards for a TD (Chris Blewitt KICK)
videos.headline: Peterman threads it to Weah in the back of the end zone

videos.description: Zack Mahoney pass complete to Amba Etta-Tawo for 49-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Cuse turns 4th and 6 into six.
